00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:59.600
I mislim

00:04:59.600 --> 00:05:01.000
da upravo to što

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:03.760
sam uvijek imao

00:05:03.760 --> 00:05:05.420
ono koliko treba,

00:05:06.020 --> 00:05:07.440
a želio sam malo više,

00:05:08.920 --> 00:05:09.400
da je

00:05:09.400 --> 00:05:11.340
to na neki način bilo presudno

00:05:11.340 --> 00:05:12.960
u svim budućim mojim

00:05:12.960 --> 00:05:14.580
aktivnostima.

00:05:15.020 --> 00:05:17.300
Možda do 15. 16. godine nisam se posebno

00:05:18.660 --> 00:05:19.520
istico

00:05:19.520 --> 00:05:20.640
niti sa svojim

00:05:20.640 --> 00:05:23.380
