00:05:23.500 --> 00:05:25.140
niti sam imao nikakve vizije.

00:05:25.220 --> 00:05:26.880
Mislim da je to zapravo i normalno

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:27.720
u tim godinama,

00:05:28.860 --> 00:05:30.740
ali već od tog

00:05:30.740 --> 00:05:33.340
neke druge faze puberteta

00:05:33.340 --> 00:05:34.800
