00:59:17.320 --> 00:59:19.320
onda mi je bilo puno jasnije

00:59:19.320 --> 00:59:21.320
zašto je Ivo Andrić dobio Nobelovu nagradu

00:59:21.320 --> 00:59:23.320
za tu knjigu

00:59:23.320 --> 00:59:25.320
i način opisati

00:59:25.320 --> 00:59:27.320
ljude, događaje u tom velikom

00:59:27.320 --> 00:59:29.320
jednom vremenskom

00:59:29.320 --> 00:59:31.320
intervalu

00:59:31.320 --> 00:59:33.320
to je prosto

00:59:33.320 --> 00:59:35.320
nevjerojatno

00:59:35.320 --> 00:59:37.320
